column5: Hi Guys, was thinkin about catching the morning bite tomorrow. Two issues though don't no exactly where to go on the lake and also don't have an auger anyone interested in going let me know. I live in Oshawa and would like to be on the ice for 6:30 7 and be gone by 9 9:30 depending on how the bite is.  Thanks Geoff  Call me at home 905-579-6704
